Fri Feb  5 01:05:43 1999  Theodore Y. Ts'o  <tytso@mit.edu>

	* ccdefname.c (get_from_os): On the Windows platform,
		automatically generate the correct default cache name
		based on what krb5_cc_dfl_ops is set to.

